dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Shawano County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2021. [Roads: Shawano County Wisconsin County-wide transportation centerline layer. ROW: The layer depicts the road right of ways in Shawano County. The data is constantly changing as roads are newly constructed, abandoned, or altered. The layer is updated when new deeds or surveys are available, as well as a backlog of older surveys and plats.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
